Program: Start the Week
Title: 30/11/2009
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b00p1nm0
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 30 Nov 2009
Andrew Marr explores how terrorism ends with strategist Audrey Kurth Cronin and police chief Sir Hugh Orde. Eugene Rogan charts the history of the Arabs, from the Ottoman Empire to the rise of Arab nationalism and the conflict between secular and Islamic values. Documentary maker Sarah Wood explains why she wanted to recreate the missing Palestinian Archive. Show less